Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/net/tor/Makefile

Package: tor
Version: 0.4.5.10-1
Depends: +libc +USE_GLIBC:librt +USE_GLIBC:libpthread +libevent2 +libopenssl +libpthread +librt +zlib +libcap
Conflicts: tor-basic
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: tor-basic
Build-Variant: full
Section: net
Category: Network
Repository: base
Title: Tor routing daemon (full)
Maintainer: Hauke Mehrtens <hauke@hauke-m.de> Peter Wagner <tripolar@gmx.at>
Require-User: tor=52:tor=52
Source: tor-0.4.5.10.tar.gz
LicenseFiles: LICENSE
Type: ipkg
Description: Tor is a toolset for a wide range of organizations and people that want to
improve their safety and security on the Internet. Using Tor can help you
anonymize web browsing and publishing, instant messaging, IRC, SSH, and
more. Tor also provides a platform on which software developers can build
new applications with built-in anonymity, safety, and privacy features.

This package contains the full tor daemon.

https://www.torproject.org/
Hauke Mehrtens <hauke@hauke-m.de> Peter Wagner <tripolar@gmx.at>
@@

